The documentation is available here: http://djv.sourceforge.net/djvHelp.html

The change list is available here: http://djv.sourceforge.net/djvChangeList.html

The copyright and license are available here: http://djv.sourceforge.net/djvLegal.html

Source code is available from Git: git clone git://git.code.sf.net/p/djv/git djv-git

Instructions for building DJV from source are in CMakeLists.txt.

To generate the developer documentation run Doxygen from the top-level
directory.
